summary: Wall-size painting of a werewolf howling hand made
descriptionHtml:
WEREWOLF WALL ART PAINTING

Mesh made by: Cancerous
Painting fully made by Me

this is meant for werewolf homes, a frameless full wall painted in werewolf howling.

HOW TO USE:
1- Extract meshes / textures in the correspondent folder of the data
2- Duplicate elk antlers,
3- click edit, add the mesh of my folder.
4- done

PERMISIONS
You can use this in anything you want as long as you credit me and link back, DO NOT REUPLOAD ANYWHERE ELSE be respectful to artists.
author: JockrisLatour
